'''Yamen''' naɣ '''Tagduda n Yamen''' (Taɛrabt : Al-Jumhuriyah al-Yamaniyah, ﺍﻟﺠﻤﻬﻮﺭﯾّﺔ اليمنية), d tamurt taɛrabt i d-yezgan af yixf deg wenẓul-ataram n [[Tazunegzirt Taɛrabt|Taɛraba]] (Arabie), tamanaɣt-is d [[Ṣenɛa]]. Ɣur-es tiftisin akwd [[Agaraw Ahendi|Ugaraw Ahendi]] d [[Ilel Azeggaɣ|Yilel Azeggaɣ]]. 
Yamen yebḍa tilisa-nes d [[Tgelda Tasaɛudit|Tagelda Tasaɛudit]] deg ugafa d [[Ɛuman]] g wegmuḍ, tesɛa tajumma taɣrudt n 527 970 km². 

Zikenni, Yamen yettwassen ddaw isem n Taɛraba Tumart (Arabie Heureuse), Yamen n wass-a yillul-d deg useggwas n 1990 sakkin tadukli n [[Tagduda Tagdudant d Taɣerfant n Yamen|Tegduda Tagdudant d Taɣerfant n Yamen]] (Yamen n Wenẓul) d [[Tagduda Taɛrabt n Yamen|Tegduda Taɛrabt n Yamen]] (Yamen n Ugafa).

